scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: This series contains material produced by IBT Local 568 and related unions dating from 1947-2011. Included are contracts, agreements, company files, correspondence, meeting minutes, newsletters, dues ledgers, handbooks and a variety of other materials related to the union's operation and organizing activities. Also of note are materials related to The Real Teamsters Caucus, Teamsters for a Democratic Union, and the Local 568 "Justice for Hoffa" Committee.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: This series is organized into two subseries, Subseries 1: Published Agreements and Subseries 2: Negotiation and Agreements.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: This subseries contains published, pamphlet-style labor contracts and agreements dating from 1949-2011. Included are National Master Freight agreements and regional supplements, IBT Local 568 agreements, regional and state-wide agreements, and other miscellaneous IBT local union agreements.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: This subseries contains files of IBT Local 568 from 1970-1995 arranged by company or type. In addition to Local 568 the subseries also contains agreements with IBT Locals 391 and 891, as well as various AFL local unions. Included are many original signed labor agreements, as well as related negotiation materials, meeting minutes and correspondence. Also of note are National Master Freight Agreements and Southern Conference Area Agreements.
